A method of applying and securing mirror mounts to the inboard surfaces of windshields. The method includes using means for optically scanning the surface of the windshield and detecting the presence of antenna wires or other markings therein to be used as reference points for the placement of a mirror mount on the windshield. The method also includes using means responsive to such detecting means for placing and affixing a mirror mount on the windshield in a desired region thereon.